526
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:55,420
I'll think about it.

527
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:57,820
Can I borrow your phone for a moment?

528
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:04,070
I've already saved my number for you.

529
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:07,390
If you make up your mind, feel free to contact me.

