00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:11,420
   

531
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:17,840
I've heard this senior is quite the tough one.

532
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:20,420
Well, seeing is believing.

533
00:31:20,420 --> 00:31:21,910
Let's go.

534
00:31:21,910 --> 00:31:24,660
- Where to? 
 - Check out the club recruitment.

535
00:31:27,220 --> 00:31:28,910
Class dismissed.

536
00:31:37,890 --> 00:31:40,700
 First, you have to take the initiative. 

537
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:43,970
 - Then? 
 - Make sure he knows you like him. 

538
00:31:43,970 --> 00:31:48,260
 You two will be far away from home with no parents around to watch over you, 

539
00:31:48,260 --> 00:31:51,070
 and there will be plenty of chances for you to study together. 

540
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:53,500
 Isn't that your opportunity? 

541
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:02,680
Jing, is there any club you're interested in?

542
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:05,540
I haven't decided yet. I'll take a look first.

543
00:32:06,600 --> 00:32:08,450
Zhou Ye! Zhou Ye!

544
00:32:08,450 --> 00:32:09,740
Here.

545
00:32:09,740 --> 00:32:11,560
Lin.

546
00:32:13,310 --> 00:32:15,420
You're done.

547
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:21,070
I sent you a message just now. Why didn't you reply?

548
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:24,982
I was busy filling out the form and didn't see it.

549
00:32:24,982 --> 00:32:27,590
Your friend joined the sports department. Consider it.

550
00:32:27,590 --> 00:32:30,590
You can mention that you're good at martial arts.

551
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:32,400
Oh, I almost forgot.

552
00:32:33,450 --> 00:32:36,040
Also, you're a sports lover.

553
00:32:36,040 --> 00:32:38,040
Sports lover.

554
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:41,870
Write that you want to use this opportunity to make new friends.

555
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:48,550
Sports department?

556
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:49,830
What's in it for you?

557
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:54,040
Do you want to lead the charge during Sports Day, starting with a 1,500m run?

558
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:55,350
No.

559
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:59,120
Tian Chi told me the sports department is pretty chill.

560
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:04,560
I think you're just blinded by a pretty face.

561
00:33:05,550 --> 00:33:07,784
Not again.

562
00:33:07,784 --> 00:33:09,020
Li.

563
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:10,360
Which club did you join?

564
00:33:10,360 --> 00:33:12,580
The student council's art department.

565
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,500
The arts department?

566
00:33:14,500 --> 00:33:15,800
Nice choice.

567
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:18,180
Don't even try to leave.

568
00:33:18,180 --> 00:33:19,910
Lu.

569
00:33:19,910 --> 00:33:26,210
I have a feeling that Tian Chi likes you.

570
00:33:26,210 --> 00:33:29,460
Tian Chi is the most handsome guy on campus.

571
00:33:29,460 --> 00:33:34,350
He's in the top three of his major and has published in a core journal with his supervisor.

572
00:33:34,350 --> 00:33:37,450
He's even been recommended by a professor for a postgraduate spot.

573
00:33:37,450 --> 00:33:39,910
He's such a perfect guy.

574
00:33:39,910 --> 00:33:42,640
What a catch!

575
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,840
Stop talking nonsense.

576
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:45,720
Who's talking nonsense?

577
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:48,840
At the start of the semester, didn't he help you carry your luggage

578
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:50,480
and give you his contact?

579
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:52,560
That's just because we went to the same high school.

580
00:33:52,560 --> 00:33:54,840
- We're alumni. 
 - Then why did he

581
00:33:54,840 --> 00:33:58,360
accompany you to the club recruitment today?

582
00:33:58,360 --> 00:33:59,870
He didn't accompany me.

583
00:33:59,870 --> 00:34:01,310
We just ran into each other.

584
00:34:01,310 --> 00:34:04,830
He ran into so many people, but why did he only accompany you?

585
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:06,360
Li, am I right?

586
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:08,870
- Yes. 
 - Look.

587
00:34:08,870 --> 00:34:12,270
People pursuing Qiu Li are lining up from the West Campus to the East Campus.

588
00:34:12,270 --> 00:34:13,710
Even she thinks I have a point.

589
00:34:13,710 --> 00:34:15,830
What do you have to say now?

590
00:34:15,830 --> 00:34:20,310
According to your logic, shouldn't he like Qiu Li instead?

591
00:34:20,310 --> 00:34:23,780
Stop right there! He's not my type.

592
00:34:33,830 --> 00:34:35,420
Why are you turning off the air con?

593
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:36,920
It's not that hot.

594
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:38,920
I think we should just turn on the fan.

595
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:41,331
Why use a fan when we have an air con?

596
00:34:41,331 --> 00:34:44,600
With the air con on, the temperature inside gets too low while it's hot outside.

597
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:46,600
If we keep going in and out, we'll catch a cold.

598
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:48,880
Plus, it wastes electricity.

599
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:52,420
Well, if you don't want to split the air con bill

600
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:55,920
because you're not here often, I'll pay for it myself.

601
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:59,680
However, I get to decide when it's on.

602
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:04,830
Why do you always boss people around?

603
00:35:04,830 --> 00:35:06,960
Just because you have money?

604
00:35:07,760 --> 00:35:09,867
What does this have to do with money?

605
00:35:09,867 --> 00:35:12,720
Can you stop making all of us suffer just because of you?

606
00:35:12,720 --> 00:35:14,340
It's fine.

607
00:35:14,340 --> 00:35:16,350
It's not that hot. We don't have to turn it on.

608
00:35:16,350 --> 00:35:18,680
Yes, we can wait until it gets hotter.

609
00:35:18,680 --> 00:35:20,230
Here, eat something.

610
00:35:20,230 --> 00:35:21,670
Don't be angry.

611
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:24,460
Go ahead and sweat if you like.

612
00:35:24,460 --> 00:35:26,620
Li, you...

613
00:35:32,770 --> 00:35:34,390
Your phone.

614
00:35:35,620 --> 00:35:37,540
Let me take this call.

615
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:45,420
Hello? Qi Qi.

616
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:47,710
You finally remembered me.

617
00:35:47,710 --> 00:35:49,880
How's your new life?

618
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:52,980
 It's hard to explain. 

619
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:59,600
I thought university would be pretty chill, but I didn't expect so many frustrating things.

620
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:01,040
What about Jing Xi Chi?

621
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:04,080
He's something else. He actually tricked us for so long.

622
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:06,820
Exactly. Even Cong—

623
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:12,270
Let's not talk about him anymore. Let's stop.

624
00:36:13,737 --> 00:36:15,570
It's okay.

625
00:36:15,570 --> 00:36:17,110
I've let it go.

626
00:36:19,290 --> 00:36:22,270
By the way, what are you doing?

627
00:36:22,270 --> 00:36:26,450
I... I'm waiting for a classmate to eat.

628
00:36:28,070 --> 00:36:31,180
I need to stop, he just finished class.

629
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:37,080
He?

630
00:36:37,080 --> 00:36:38,870
Who is he?

631
00:37:42,890 --> 00:37:45,000
Why are you here?

632
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:48,290
You've been in the city for so long and never contacted me.

633
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:52,230
I'm just joking.

634
00:37:52,230 --> 00:37:55,260
I'm over all that.

635
00:37:55,260 --> 00:37:58,270
Since it's just the two of us studying here,

636
00:37:58,270 --> 00:38:02,350
shouldn't we look out for each other as old classmates?

637
00:38:04,500 --> 00:38:06,830
Are you free later?

638
00:38:06,830 --> 00:38:09,500
I'm free.

639
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:13,330
Then come with me to your university's screening hall for a movie.

640
00:38:13,330 --> 00:38:15,100
A movie?

641
00:38:15,100 --> 00:38:16,420
Why not?

642
00:38:16,420 --> 00:38:20,390
I rarely visit your campus. Won't you even show me around?

643
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:22,940
Okay.

644
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:24,360
Let's go.

645
00:38:45,190 --> 00:38:47,520
Who's that? Why didn't you reply?

646
00:38:47,520 --> 00:38:48,953
It's Du Wei.

647
00:38:48,953 --> 00:38:51,800
She asked if I filled out that application form.

648
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,665
Speaking of this, I'm curious.

649
00:38:53,665 --> 00:38:56,740
Isn't that competition team pretty good? Why are you so against joining?

650
00:38:56,740 --> 00:38:58,133
It's too much hassle.

651
00:38:58,133 --> 00:39:00,310
Not joining is more hassle, okay?

652
00:39:00,310 --> 00:39:03,960
Du Wei is famous for never giving up until she gets what she wants.

653
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:07,087
What's that got to do with me?

