657
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:19,670
Even if I'm the top student, that's only among freshmen.

658
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:25,210
Even if we actually join that competition, we'll just end up doing the hardest work.

659
00:39:26,750 --> 00:39:27,910
That's it?

660
00:39:27,910 --> 00:39:29,450
That's it.

