00:39:30,810 --> 00:39:34,910
Well, should I call you naive or just plain dumb?

662
00:39:34,910 --> 00:39:37,280
Haven't you noticed the way she looks at you?

663
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:39,480
It's like she's about to see right through you!

664
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:48,240
So by your logic, since you pay so much attention to her, do you like her?

665
00:39:48,240 --> 00:39:51,020
Can you not say things like that? It'll bring bad luck.

666
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:57,501
What are you doing?

667
00:39:57,501 --> 00:40:00,760
I'm working out now. I have to strictly control my daily fat intake.

668
00:40:00,760 --> 00:40:03,200
It can only be 30% of my total daily calories.

669
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:06,370
- Okay. 
 - I'll have some more of this then.

